close_reason: History scan found no confirmed private data; only intentional sanitizer fixtures and password-clearing code matched.
body: "Audit approach:\n- Search every revision with git grep for common token, private-key, password, secret, and credential patterns.\n- Enumerate filenames across all revisions looking for env files, private keys, credentials, token files, and secret material.\n- Treat test fixture words such as token=secret as non-findings when they are synthetic and intentionally used to verify sanitization behavior."
